  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You infuse your chakra into your ammo set with a trigger to erupt into a lethal explosion. For the next minute your ammo stack inflicts a rank of Primed on each successful weapon or Taijutsu attack from the ammo stack. A creature cannot have more than 10 ranks Primed. As a Bonus Action or a Reaction, you can detonate all Primed ranks on all creatures you can see, dealing 2d12 Force damage for every prime stack detonated. A creature can spend an action on their turn to make a Sleight of Hand check versus your Taijutsu Save DC to remove all ranks of Primed on them. You cannot detonate the stacks of Primed a creature has as a reaction while they are taking this action.</p>",
